text.section:
In a circuit court, an arrest warrant shall be issued on a form that:
Is 8 1/2 by 11 inches in size;
Contains the following information, if known, about the person for whom the warrant is issued:
Full name;
Last address;
Race;
Sex;
Height;
Weight;
Hair color;
Eye color;
Driver's license number;
Social Security number;
Distinguishing body marks or scars; and
Any other pertinent identifying information; and
Contains specific instructions to indicate the judge or court commissioner before whom the person is directed to appear once arrested.

An arrest warrant issued under this section shall be clearly captioned:
"Arrest warrant/State capias";
"Arrest warrant/contempt";
"Arrest warrant/contempt of court"; or
"Arrest warrant/body attachment".
